  HONESTY FLAG: Arm A residual is zero by an algebraic identity on Omega<=2 windows (F(a/q) = M'(a/q) exactly, since e(n a/q) is constant on classes mod q). The pre-registered 'signal' is therefore VACUOUS as an empirical finding: it holds as a theorem, in the strongest possible form (residual exactly 0, not merely <= 1.35). Empirical content lives in the supplementary Arms B and C above, which carry NO pre-registered verdict.
